  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\"><img alt=\"House Lothston.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/50px-House_Lothston.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/75px-House_Lothston.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/100px-House_Lothston.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Jeyne Lothston</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\"><img alt=\"House Lothston.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/50px-House_Lothston.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/75px-House_Lothston.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/100px-House_Lothston.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jeyne_Lothston.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jeyne Lothston.jpg\" src=\"/images/5/59/Jeyne_Lothston.jpg\" width=\"292\" height=\"560\" /></a><div>Jeyne Lothston, by Magali Villeneuve as depicted in <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>.</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\">House Lothston</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_164_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">164&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Fathers</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lucas_Lothston_(husband_of_Falena)\" title=\"Lucas Lothston (husband of Falena)\">Lucas Lothston</a> <small>(officially)</small></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a> <small>(rumored)</small></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Falena_Stokeworth\" title=\"Falena Stokeworth\">Falena Stokeworth</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\nKing <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jeyne Lothston</b> was a noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\">House Lothston</a> and the daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucas_Lothston_(husband_of_Falena)\" title=\"Lucas Lothston (husband of Falena)\">Lucas Lothston</a> and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Falena_Stokeworth\" title=\"Falena Stokeworth\">Falena Stokeworth</a>. She was King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a>'s eighth mistress, and rumored to have been possibly fathered by the king himself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Lothston&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jeyne was brought to court by her mother, <a href=\"/index.php/Falena_Stokeworth\" title=\"Falena Stokeworth\">Falena Stokeworth</a>, in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_178_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">178&#160;AC</a>, when she was fourteen. King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon the Unworthy</a> made Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucas_Lothston_(husband_of_Falena)\" title=\"Lucas Lothston (husband of Falena)\">Lucas Lothston</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> his new <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand</a>, and it was said (but never proved) that he enjoyed mother and daughter together in the same bed. Aegon soon gave Jeyne a <a href=\"/index.php/Pox\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pox\">pox</a> he had caught from the <a href=\"/index.php/Whores\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whores\">whores</a> he had seen after Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Bracken\" title=\"Bethany Bracken\">Bethany Bracken</a>'s execution, and the Lothstons were then all sent from court.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Lothston&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">Hedge<br />knight</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><s